description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a part 3, 5 and 6 storey  building (Block A) fronting Regents Canal, a part 6 and 8 storey building (Block B) on the corner of Queensbridge Road and Whiston Road and a 5 storey building (Block C) adjacent to the eastern boundary, together providing 1760 sq m business floorspace (Class B1) and 131 residential units comprising 47x 1 bed, 48 x 2 bed and 36 x 3 bed flats, 36 of which are affordable housing units, together with the provision of 98 car parking spaces and 100 bicycle spaces in the basement.
